---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
export const prerender = true;
const title = "Cookie Policy \u2014 Numetal";
const description = "Cookie Policy for numetal.xyz. Only strictly-necessary Cloudflare security cookies are used \u2014 no advertising, analytics, or tracking, and no consent banner required.";
const canonical = "https://numetal.xyz/cookies";
const bodyHtml = `<style>
  :root{--bgray:#e7e7e7;--ikb:#002FA7;--paper:#FAFAF8;--ink:#141414;--cyan:#0791a6;--hard:#8c8c8c;--orange:#FF5A1F;--line:#cfcfcf;--muted:#7c7c7c;--mono:ui-monospace,'SF Mono','SFMono-Regular',Menlo,Consolas,monospace;--sans:'Helvetica Neue',Helvetica,Arial,'Liberation Sans',sans-serif}
  *{box-sizing:border-box;margin:0;padding:0}
  html{-webkit-font-smoothing:antialiased}
  body{background:var(--bgray);color:var(--ink);font-family:var(--sans);font-size:15px;line-height:1.6;min-height:100vh;display:flex;flex-direction:column}
  a{color:var(--ikb)}
  .wrap{width:100%;max-width:760px;margin:0 auto;padding:0 24px}
  .dither{height:11px;background-image:radial-gradient(#191919 .62px,transparent .72px);background-size:3px 3px}
  .top{display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;padding:16px 24px 8px;position:sticky;top:29px;z-index:190;background:#fff;border-bottom:1px solid var(--line)}
  nav{display:flex;gap:16px;font-size:13px;align-items:center}
  nav a{color:var(--ink);text-decoration:none}
  .stamp{font-family:var(--mono);font-size:11px;letter-spacing:.12em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--muted);padding:6px 24px 0}
  .stamp b{color:var(--ikb);font-weight:700}
  .mark{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:9px;font-family:var(--mono);font-weight:700;letter-spacing:.06em}
  .mark a{color:var(--ink);text-decoration:none}
  .mark .sq{width:13px;height:13px;background:var(--ikb)}
  .tagh{font-family:var(--mono);font-size:11px;letter-spacing:.1em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--muted)}
  main{flex:1;padding:48px 0 64px}
  h1{font-family:var(--mono);font-size:32px;letter-spacing:-.01em;margin-bottom:6px}
  .upd{font-family:var(--mono);font-size:12px;color:var(--muted);margin-bottom:30px}
  h2{font-family:var(--mono);font-size:14px;letter-spacing:.03em;text-transform:uppercase;margin:30px 0 10px;display:flex;gap:9px;align-items:center}
  h2 .n{color:var(--ikb)}
  p,li{margin-bottom:12px;color:#222}
  ul{padding-left:20px}
  strong{color:var(--ink)}
  table{width:100%;border-collapse:collapse;margin:14px 0;font-size:13px}
  th,td{border:1px solid var(--line);padding:9px 11px;text-align:left;vertical-align:top}
  th{font-family:var(--mono);font-size:11px;letter-spacing:.04em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--muted);background:#fff}
  code{font-family:var(--mono);font-size:13px;background:#f0f0ec;padding:1px 5px}
  .note{border:1px solid var(--ink);padding:16px 18px;margin:8px 0;font-size:14px}
  footer{background:#fff;margin-top:40px;border-top:1px solid var(--ink)}
  .foot{display:flex;justify-content:space-between;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:12px;font-size:11px;color:var(--muted);padding:22px 0}
  .foot a{color:var(--muted)}
  .flinks{display:flex;gap:14px;flex-wrap:wrap;justify-content:flex-end}
  .foot a{color:var(--muted)}
  .sheet{max-width:880px;margin:0 auto;background:#fff;border-left:1px solid var(--line);border-right:1px solid var(--line);min-height:100vh;display:flex;flex-direction:column}
  .social{display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:14px}
  .social a{display:inline-flex;color:inherit;line-height:0;text-decoration:none}
  .social a:hover{color:var(--ikb)}
  .social svg{width:17px;height:17px;fill:currentColor;display:block}
</style>

<div class="sheet">
  <div class="top">
    <div class="mark"><span class="sq"></span><a href="/">NUMETAL</a></div>
    <nav><a href="/blog">Blog</a><a href="/">Studio</a><a href="/fees">Fee engine</a><a href="/airdrops">Airdrops</a><a href="https://gokhan.vc" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Atelier&nbsp;↗</a></nav>
  </div>
  <div class="stamp">Doc · <b>Cookies</b> · Base · legal</div>
<div class="dither"></div>

<main><div class="wrap">
  <h1>Cookie Policy</h1>
  <div class="upd">Last updated: 11 June 2026</div>

  <div class="note">numetal.xyz uses <strong>no advertising, analytics, profiling, or cross-site tracking cookies</strong>, embeds no third-party marketing pixels, and loads no consent-management platform. The only cookies that may be set are <strong>strictly necessary security cookies</strong> placed by our infrastructure provider, Cloudflare, to protect the site against bots and abuse and to deliver content.</div>

  <h2><span class="n">01</span>Why there is no consent banner</h2>
  <p>Under Article 5(3) of the ePrivacy Directive (2002/58/EC) and its national transpositions — UK PECR reg. 6(4), Germany's TDDDG §25(2), and France via the CNIL — <strong>strictly necessary cookies are exempt from prior consent</strong>. Because the site sets only such cookies and no non-essential storage, GDPR's consent machinery is not triggered. Our obligation is <strong>transparency</strong>, met by this page — not a consent prompt. Adding a banner would itself introduce unnecessary storage, so we deliberately do not.</p>

  <h2><span class="n">02</span>Cookies that may be set</h2>
  <table>
    <thead><tr><th>Cookie</th><th>Set by</th><th>Purpose</th><th>Duration</th><th>Type / legal basis</th></tr></thead>
    <tbody>
      <tr><td><code>__cf_bm</code></td><td>Cloudflare</td><td>Bot management — distinguishes humans from automated traffic to protect the site. Not used for advertising or cross-site tracking.</td><td>~30 min (rolling)</td><td>Strictly necessary — exempt from consent (ePrivacy Art 5(3)); security processing under GDPR Art 6(1)(f)</td></tr>
      <tr><td><code>cf_clearance</code></td><td>Cloudflare</td><td>Stores the result of a security challenge so a verified visitor is not re-challenged on every request.</td><td>~30 min</td><td>Strictly necessary — exempt from consent; GDPR Art 6(1)(f)</td></tr>
      <tr><td><code>__cflb</code> / <code>cf_use_ob</code></td><td>Cloudflare</td><td>Session routing for load balancing (may not appear on this site).</td><td>Session / short-lived</td><td>Strictly necessary — exempt from consent</td></tr>
    </tbody>
  </table>

  <h2><span class="n">03</span>What we do not do</h2>
  <p>We set <strong>no first-party Numetal cookies</strong>. We do not sell or share any data derived from these cookies, and we do not use them for advertising, profiling, or targeted advertising (CCPA/CPRA). The read-only fee dashboard at <a href="/fees">/fees</a> reads public on-chain data from the Base network through fixed server-side endpoints; it does not set tracking cookies in your browser and does not build a profile of you.</p>

  <h2><span class="n">04</span>Managing cookies</h2>
  <p>Because these cookies are strictly necessary, blocking them in your browser may break security challenges and prevent the site from loading. You can still delete them at any time via your browser settings. For how Cloudflare processes request data, see Cloudflare's cookie documentation and privacy policy.</p>

  <h2><span class="n">05</span>Contact</h2>
  <p>Questions about cookies or privacy: <strong>contact@numetal.xyz</strong>. See also our <a href="/privacy">Privacy Policy</a>.</p>
</div></main>

<footer><div class="wrap foot">
  <span>Numetal · an Atelier Gökhan studio · on Base</span>
